<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span><span class="c5">عن:</span> النبي <span class="special">﵌</span>.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">وعنه:</span> أبو عبد الله.<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
